{"tid":1810344,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會拍拖拍到我咁","createTime":"2020-01-03T19:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T02:43:17.000Z","uid":335789,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf4b678989084f0b0165b724ef7ce82cb8d2896","tid":1810344,"uid":335789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:27:17.000Z","msg":"大約喺一個月前 有親人過身 有好多身後事要搞 心情好差 咁啱喺嗰幾日 同男朋友嘈到冷戰咗兩日 最後我揾佢氹番佢 其實已經有啲灰心但當冇野 因為唔想又嘈啊..<br />\n<br />\n平安夜嗰日又嘈多獲 又係冷戰左日半 第二日聖誕節我揾番佢約佢出黎 覺得唔想連節日都搞到咁 表面上冇野 但其實積埋積埋都幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次咁樣做主動其實都幾攰 嗰種覺得不被重視嘅感覺有冇人明 宜家個心已經好淡好攰...但我仲好愛佢 可以點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39ccd41ece36abe30afe5d4b19d93d36f82bc88","tid":1810344,"uid":76678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:28:55.000Z","msg":"分"},{"pid":"54cb9896ca132eed8182b1823bb59746a61aeaad","tid":1810344,"uid":7831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:31:23.000Z","msg":"你個Case咁似我同我女友發生嘅事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c461e38f04b68aaac5fabfd651b9eb4f40ad64a","tid":1810344,"uid":224741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:31:55.000Z","msg":"朋友之間都係咁，自己無被重視一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我解答唔到方法，但是我早習慣左自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4b5b569315f17013275153e027093d5b581785","tid":1810344,"uid":4422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:32:36.000Z","msg":"咁睇落你男朋友好似唔係太重視你"},{"pid":"416e38fd487eeb167800cecfa697ab15163fb2fb","tid":1810344,"uid":7831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:35:07.000Z","msg":"有冇同佢傾過個問題<br />\n我同女友鬧交之後儲會搵返個問題<br />\n同埋講埋解決方法<br />\n好多時都係我重複犯錯激嬲佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我愛你阿女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},